property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
WITH "CTE_Plant" AS (
    SELECT
        "HR_ALL_ORGANIZATION_UNITS"."ORGANIZATION_ID"       AS "ORGANIZATION_ID",
        "HR_ALL_ORGANIZATION_UNITS"."NAME"                  AS "NAME",
        "HR_ALL_ORGANIZATION_UNITS"."LOCATION_ID"           AS "LOCATION_ID",
        "ORG_ORGANIZATION_DEFINITIONS"."ORGANIZATION_CODE"  AS "ORGANIZATION_CODE"
    FROM "ORG_ORGANIZATION_DEFINITIONS" AS "ORG_ORGANIZATION_DEFINITIONS"
        LEFT JOIN "HR_ALL_ORGANIZATION_UNITS" AS "HR_ALL_ORGANIZATION_UNITS"
            ON "ORG_ORGANIZATION_DEFINITIONS"."ORGANIZATION_ID" = "HR_ALL_ORGANIZATION_UNITS"."ORGANIZATION_ID"
    WHERE NULLIF(CAST("HR_ALL_ORGANIZATION_UNITS"."ORGANIZATION_ID" AS VARCHAR(255)), '') IS NOT NULL
)
SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || CAST("Plant"."ORGANIZATION_ID" AS VARCHAR(255)) AS "ID",
    CAST("Plant"."ORGANIZATION_CODE" AS VARCHAR(255))                            AS "PlantNumber",
    "Plant"."NAME"                                                               AS "PlantName",
    "HR_LOCATIONS_ALL"."COUNTRY"                                                 AS "Country",
    "FND_TERRITORIES"."NLS_TERRITORY"                                            AS "CountryName",
    <%=sourceSystem%>                                                            AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "CTE_Plant" AS "Plant"
    INNER JOIN "HR_LOCATIONS_ALL" AS "HR_LOCATIONS_ALL"
        ON "Plant"."LOCATION_ID" = "HR_LOCATIONS_ALL"."LOCATION_ID"
    LEFT JOIN "FND_TERRITORIES" AS "FND_TERRITORIES"
        ON "HR_LOCATIONS_ALL"."COUNTRY" = "FND_TERRITORIES"."TERRITORY_CODE"

WITH "CTE_Plant" AS (
    SELECT 
        DISTINCT 
        "OrganizationUnitPVO"."OrganizationId"                              AS "OrganizationId",
        "OrganizationUnitPVO"."OrganizationUnitTranslationPEOName"          AS "OrganizationUnitTranslationPEOName",
        "OrganizationUnitPVO"."OrganizationUnitPEOLocationId"               AS "OrganizationUnitPEOLocationId",
        "ItemPVO"."ItemOrganizationParameterPEOOrganizationCode"            AS "ItemOrganizationParameterPEOOrganizationCode"
    FROM "FscmTopModelAM_OrganizationAM_OrganizationUnitPVO" AS "OrganizationUnitPVO"
        LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_EgpItemsPublicModelAM_Item" AS "ItemPVO"
            ON "OrganizationUnitPVO"."OrganizationId" = "ItemPVO"."ItemOrganizationParameterPEOOrganizationId")
SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "Plant"."OrganizationId" AS "ID",
    "Location"."LocationPEOInternalLocationCode"          AS "PlantNumber",
    "Plant"."OrganizationUnitTranslationPEOName"          AS "PlantName",
    "Location"."AddressesPEOCountry"                      AS "Country",
    "Territory"."NlsTerritory"                            AS "CountryName",
    <%=sourceSystem%>                                     AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "CTE_Plant" AS "Plant"
         LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_LocationAM_HRLocationsPVO" AS "Location"
                   ON "Plant"."OrganizationUnitPEOLocationId" = "Location"."LocationPEOLocationId"
         LEFT JOIN "FscmTopModelAM_FinExtractAM_AnalyticsExtractServiceAM_TerritoriesPVO" AS "Territory"
                   ON "Location"."AddressesPEOCountry" = "Territory"."TerritoryCode"

SELECT <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "T001W"."MANDT" || '::' || "T001W"."WERKS"     AS "ID",
    "T001W"."WERKS"                                                                AS "PlantNumber",
    "T001W"."NAME1"                                                                AS "PlantName",
    "T001W"."LAND1"                                                                AS "Country",
    "T005T"."LANDX"                                                                AS "CountryName",
    <%=sourceSystem%> || '::' || "T001W"."MANDT"                                   AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "T001W" AS "T001W"
    LEFT JOIN "T005T" AS "T005T"
        ON "T001W"."MANDT" = "T005T"."MANDT"
            AND "T001W"."LAND1" = "T005T"."LAND1"
            AND "T005T"."SPRAS" = <%=LanguageKey%> 
WHERE NULLIF("T001W"."MANDT", '') IS NOT NULL

SELECT
    ID,
    COUNT(*) AS rc
FROM (


SELECT
    <%=sourceSystem%>||'::'||"PartyContactsV3".LocationId                  AS ID,
	"CDSPostalAddressHistoryV2".CountryRegionId                            AS Country,
    "PartyContactsV3".Description                                          AS CountryText,
    "OperationalSitesV2".SiteId                                            AS PlantName,
    "OperationalSitesV2".SiteId                                            AS PlantNumber,
    NULL                                                                   AS CountryName,
    NULL                                                                   AS SourceSystemInstance
FROM "PartyContactsV3"
	LEFT JOIN "CDSPostalAddressHistoryV2" 
	ON "PartyContactsV3".LocationId = "CDSPostalAddressHistoryV2".LocationId
    LEFT JOIN "OperationalSitesV2"
    ON "OperationalSitesV2".PrimaryAddressZipCode = "CDSPostalAddressHistoryV2".ZipCode



) t
GROUP BY ID
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
order by COUNT(*) desc
